Paper: hep-th/9409139

Date: 1994-09-23

Title: Supersymmetry and the Geometry of Taub-NUT

Authors: J.W. van Holten (NIKHEF-H)

Comments: 9 pages, NIKHEF-H/94-29

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B342 (1995) 47-52

The supersymmetric extension of Taub-NUT space admits 4 standardsupersymmetries plus several additional non-standard ones. The geometricalorigin of these symmetries is traced. The result has applications to fermionmodes in gravitational instantons as well as in long-range monopole dynamics.